<![CDATA[<font face="arial" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial;" size="2">Hello&nbsp;{!Contact.FirstName},</font><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial;"><font size="2"><br></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial;"><font face="arial" size="2">As I am sure you are aware, the ELD mandate is fast approaching.&nbsp;Fleets have until <b>December 18, 2017</b> to implement electronic logging devices, thus eliminating paper logs. There's no doubt that there will be many fleets who wait until the last minute to comply with this mandate. This could not only lead to supply issues, but also put your drivers at a disadvantage when they have to adopt the new technology immediately. Acting now gives your drivers time to learn the technology while continuing to use their paper logs.&nbsp;</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial;"><font face="arial" size="2"><br></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial;"><font face="arial" size="2">TruckersB2B has partnered with several ELD providers to meet your needs and budget. We also have some attractive&nbsp;offers for those who act early, including free months of service, special pricing, and free tablets!</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial;"><font face="arial" size="2"><br></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial;"><font face="arial" size="2"><a href="http://benefits.truckersb2b.com/eld/?utm_source=SF">Learn more about our providers and the special incentives.</a></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial;"><font size="2"><br></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial;"><font size="2">I'd love to put you in touch with one <i>or all </i>of our providers to help you find the best solution for your fleet. You can either complete the form <a href="http://benefits.truckersb2b.com/eld/?utm_source=SF">on this page</a>, call me directly, or reply to this email.&nbsp;</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial;"><font size="2"><br></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial;"><font size="2">Thank you for your time,</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial;"><font size="2"><br></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial;"><div style=""><font size="2">{!User.FirstName} {!User.LastName}&nbsp;</font></div><div style=""><font size="2">{!User.Title}&nbsp;</font></div><div style=""><font size="2">{!User.Phone}&nbsp;</font></div><div style=""><font size="2">{!User.Email}&nbsp;</font></div></div>]]></td>
